---
description: Conventional PR titles for graphql-gene
alwaysApply: true
---

Do not add new scopes to `.github/workflows/pull-request-title.yml` to make a title pass. If no allowed scope fits the change, use a scope-free title instead, for example:

- `refactor: rename list pagination args to skip and limit`
- `feat: add association list wrapper`
- `fix: correct offset handling`
- `ci: adjust workflow condition`
- `docs: update plugin README`
